snippet.title: Battle Wizard Attack - Official Trailer (Early Access)
snippet.description:
Battle Wizard Attack - Early Access starts August 30th 2024
Official Launch Trailer (Early Access)

Unleash your inner spell caster in this action-packed, retro-style RPG! Choose from eight powerful magic disciplines and face monstrous hordes across sprawling maps packed with destructible chaos.

Battle Wizard Attack was supported by BMWK & MBB

Wishlist now on Steam.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2621160?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=trailer&utm_medium=trailer
